					<!-- cd-faq-content --></li>

				<li><a class="cd-faq-trigger" href="#0">How do I sign up?</a>
					<div class="cd-faq-content">
						<p>Using the menu bar to the left, you can select 'Register'
						and fill out the form. After successfully completing the form,
						you will be sent an email instructing you how to confirm your account.</p>
					</div> <!-- cd-faq-content --></li>

				<li><a class="cd-faq-trigger" href="#0">Can I remove a
						comment?</a>
					<div class="cd-faq-content">
						<p>Comments are managed by our Administrators. If the course is currently
						running, you can edit or remove your comment by accessing it through your dashboard.</p>
					</div> <!-- cd-faq-content --></li>

				<li><a class="cd-faq-trigger" href="#0">How do reviews
						work?</a>
					<div class="cd-faq-content">
						<p>The review system only grants access to registered student
							that are currently attending that specific course. As a registered
							student, you can fill out review. Each student is allowed to rate each
							course once, but while the semester is running, students can edit their reviews.</p>
					</div> <!-- cd-faq-content --></li>
			</ul>

