						<p>Using the side menu bar, follow the 'change password' link.
						If you have forgotten your password and would like to recover your
						account, follow the 'forgot password?' link.</p>
					</div> <!-- cd-faq-content --></li>

				<li><a class="cd-faq-trigger" href="#0">How do I deactivate my
						account?</a>
					<div class="cd-faq-content">
						<p>You can deactivate your account by following the link on the
						side menu of your dashboard. If you later choose to reactivate your
						account, you can do so by choosing 'active account' on the home screen</p>
					</div> <!-- cd-faq-content --></li>
<!--
